        {
            "id": "https://ui123456ax.github.io/2023/08/09/Burp%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81/",
            "url": "https://ui123456ax.github.io/2023/08/09/Burp%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81/",
            "title": "使用Burp完成广东省活动任务",
            "date_published": "2023-08-09T08:06:12.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"前言\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#前言\">#</a> 前言</h1>\n<p>转眼间暑假就已经过去一半了，但作业是一点没动（懒）<br />\n在闲的中途看到 **” 某书香经典阅读 “**，呃... 想起了！不就是语文老师布置暑假作业嘛</p>\n<details><summary>有个大胆的想法就在我脑中出现了 嘿嘿</summary><div>\n<p><code>利用BurpScript改包POST请求</code> <br />\n本来是不报有希望，但凡事都得尝试一下懂吧</p>\n</div></details>\n<h1 id=\"开始\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#开始\">#</a> 开始</h1>\n<p>目标：<strong>广东省活动榜一</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"使用burp抓包数据\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#使用burp抓包数据\">#</a> 使用 Burp 抓包数据</h2>\n<p>因为是关卡制的，随便点开一关开始抓包<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/20230809192031.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p>从这里不难看出 result_items 对应的是正常率</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"><span>h</span></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>POST /api/student/mission/v2/question/end HTTP/1.1</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>Host: api.xxxxx.com</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>Connection: close</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>Content-Length: <span class=\"token number\">231</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>referer: https://xxxxx/wx5dd5632a942cb333/41/page-frame.html</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>xweb_xhr: <span class=\"token number\">1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>user-agent: Mozilla/5.0 <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Windows NT <span class=\"token number\">10.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> Win64<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> x64<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> AppleWebKit/537.36 <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>KHTML, like Gecko<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> Chrome/107.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 MicroMessenger/7.0.20.1781<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0x6700143B<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> NetType/WIFI MiniProgramEnv/Windows WindowsWechat/WMPF XWEB/8287</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>token: xxxxx</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre>Accept: */*</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre>Sec-Fetch-Site: cross-site</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre>Sec-Fetch-Mode: cors</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre>Sec-Fetch-Dest: empty</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre>Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflate</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"15\"></td><td><pre>Accept-Language: zh-CN,zh</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"16\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"17\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">mission_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">4258343</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">chapter_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">10044</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">t_record_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">547609783</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">question_items</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%5B305187%2C305188%2C305184%2C305191%2C305181%5D<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">time_items</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%5B0.852%2C0.516%2C0.52%2C0.573%2C0.577%5D<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">result_items</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%5Bfalse%2Cfalse%2Cfalse%2Ctrue%2Cfalse%5D</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>把 False 全部改成 True，直接通关<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20230809193141.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"post攻击\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#post攻击\">#</a> POST 攻击</h2>\n<p>Ps: 后面我又抓了几个数据包发现 <code>chapter_id=xxx</code>  这个值，指的是关卡<br />\n比如 <code>chapter_id=10044</code>  是第一关，那么 <code>chapter_id=10045</code>  就是第二关<br />\n用 Repeater 看看是怎么个事<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20230809195435.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token string\">\"message\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"\"</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"code\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">200</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"data\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span><span class=\"token string\">\"this_score\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"last_score\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"flower\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> true, <span class=\"token string\">\"result\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span>, <span class=\"token string\">\"first\"</span><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">:</span> true<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>嘿嘿<br />\n发送给 Intruder，类型选择<strong> Sniper</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>POST /api/student/mission/v2/question/end HTTP/1.1</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>Host: api.xxxxx.com</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>Connection: close</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>Content-Length: <span class=\"token number\">396</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>referer: https://xxxxx/wx5dd5632a942cb333/41/page-frame.html</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre>xweb_xhr: <span class=\"token number\">1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>user-agent: Mozilla/5.0 <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Windows NT <span class=\"token number\">10.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> Win64<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> x64<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> AppleWebKit/537.36 <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>KHTML, like Gecko<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> Chrome/107.0.0.0 Safari/537.36 MicroMessenger/7.0.20.1781<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>0x6700143B<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> NetType/WIFI MiniProgramEnv/Windows WindowsWechat/WMPF XWEB/8287</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>token: xxxxx</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre>Accept: */*</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre>Sec-Fetch-Site: cross-site</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"12\"></td><td><pre>Sec-Fetch-Mode: cors</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"13\"></td><td><pre>Sec-Fetch-Dest: empty</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"14\"></td><td><pre>Accept-Encoding: gzip, deflate</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"15\"></td><td><pre>Accept-Language: zh-CN,zh</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"16\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"17\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">mission_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">4258343</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">chapter_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>§10045§<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">t_record_id</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">547640816</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">question_items</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%5B305210%2C305233%2C305227%2C305212%2C305219%2C305214%2C305225%2C305209%2C305218%2C305236%2C305231%2C305202%5D<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">time_items</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%5B0.712%2C0.578%2C0.631%2C0.575%2C0.586%2C0.581%2C0.555%2C0.636%2C1.264%2C3.754%2C4.854%2C0.702%5D<span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">result_items</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span>%5Btrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%2Ctrue%5D</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如下设置，HTTP 请求使用单线程<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20230809200511.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n很快啊，不到一会就过了十几关<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20230809201146.png\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n挂机 Loading....<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20230809201507.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<h1 id=\"最终成果\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#最终成果\">#</a> 最终成果</h1>\n<p>如下图<br />\n<img data-src=\"./%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9B%BE/%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E7%9C%81%E6%A6%9C%E4%B8%80/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20230809202448.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n",
